## Getting Started

To run this project locally:

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone git@github.com:TanaNazarevych/InteractiveHeartBeat.git
cd InteractiveHeartBeat

# 2. Install dependencies
npm install

# 3. Start the development server
npm run dev
